<SLUG> BC-ECONOMIST-BUDGET-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
   (These excellent ``separate buy'' articles are from the current
(week beginning 5 Dec. 1998) Economist magazine.)  
  
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
in Canada except to The Toronto Globe &AMP; Mail.)  
  
 (To publish these articles, they must be purchased from New York
Times Syndicate sales representative NIRDI RELIS in New York at
1-800-972-3550 or 212-499-3333, or fax her at 212-499-3382.)  
  
 (PLEASE NOTE: Each of these articles has been transmitted into the
``k'' commentary news file.)  
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; COMMENTARY &LR;  &QC; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
