   C. PREHISTORIC MEDICINE KIT The Iceman, whose mummified body was
discovered in 1991 in the Tyrolean Alps in Northern Italy, has
given scientists a lifelike picture of what people wore, ate and
carried with them on treks into the Alps, some 5,300 years ago. By
John Noble Wilford. 800 words.
