Alfred A. Knopf. $26. The diaries of a German civilian who saved
thousands during the Rape of Nanking.
</P>
<P>
   NYTBOOK-SHERIDAN-1000&AMP;ADD-NYTSF, A TRAITOR'S KISS, The Life of
Richard Brinsley Sheridan, 1751-1816. By Fintan O'Toole. 519 pp.
New York: Farrar, Straus &AMP; Giroux. $30. As an Irishman, Richard
Brinsley Sheridan was doomed to a life in the margins.
</P>
