Intimate Letters to Susan Huntington Dickinson. Edited by Ellen
Louise Hart and Martha Nell Smith. 323 pp. Ashfield, Mass.: Paris
Press. Paper, $19.95. Emily Dickinson's letters to her
sister-in-law are short, impassioned and not easy to interpret.
