<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-10 13:29 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2941 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CHILDCARE-COLUMN-2TAK     12-10 1080
