<P>
   TRAVEL-NOTES-BOS (Undated) _ One thing you can almost count on
when you revisit Walt Disney World is that something new and nifty
will have sprung up. By Richard Carpenter.
</P>
<P>
   TRAVEL-COLLINS-BOS (Fie a Sciliar, Italy) _ In your face _ the
Big D (the Dolomites) of Italy! By Bud Collins.
