BILL-BLASS-STROKE (Houston) _ New York designer Bill Blass was
admitted Thursday morning to Methodist Hospital after suffering
what doctors described as a mild stroke. The 76-year-old designer
will remain in Methodist's Intensive Care Unit for further tests
and at least 24 hours observation. By LINDA GILLAN GRIFFIN.
</P>
