<P>
   &UR; WORKWAYS  &LR; _  &UR; Question: &LR;  I'd like to move to France but don't
know how to find work there. I have an associate's degree in
landscape horticulture but am willing to take any kind of job.
Unfortunately, I don't speak French. What should I do? Columnist
Ilana DeBare has the answer
</P>
