<HEADLINE>
QUOTATION OF THE DAY
</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-IMPEACH-NYT, which moved in
``w'' news file.) 
c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``Life was so much simpler before they found that dress, wasn't
it?''
</P>
<P>
   _DAVID SCHIPPERS, counsel to the Judiciary Committee
Republicans.
</P>
