throughout the continent. (Kerwin Plevka/Houston Chronicle Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT6) MAGDEBURG, Germany -- Dec. 10, 1998 -- ADV. FOR SUN.,
DEC. 13 -- EUROPE-FOREIGNERS-1-HNS, 12-09 -- Dirk is a young
neo-Nazi skinhead who says he cannot stand the sight of non-Aryans.
A resident of the small German town of Magdeburg, he is on the
sharp edge of the anti-immigrant sentiment that is growing across
Europe. ``If we come across one or two foreigners on their own, we
beat them up,'' Dirk says. (Kerwin Plevka/Houston Chronicle Photo)
