the busy Ararat restaurant, is the second Kurd in Badolato to find
an Italian girlfriend. ``You hear of racism and skinheads in
Europe, but I've never felt any rejection in Badolato,'' he says.
``They have given us a great chance to make a home.'' (Kerwin
