 (PLEASE NOTE: This article has been transmitted into the ``f''
financial news, ``a'' domestic/general news and ``i'' international
news files.)  
  
 By PETER MCGILL  
 c.1998 Asahi News Service  
 (Distributed by New York Times Special Features)  
